#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an atlantean ware: Log, part 1
#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Log, part 1
#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a frisian ware: Log, part 1
#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an empire ware: Log, part 1
#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a barbarian ware: Log, part 1
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:74
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/atlanteans/units.lua:350
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/barbarians/units.lua:99
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/empire/units.lua:92
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/frisians/units.lua:86
msgctxt "ware"
msgid ""
"Logs are an important basic building material. They are produced by felling "
"trees."
msgstr "Els troncs són un dels materials de construcció fonamentals. S'obtenen talant arbres."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Log, part 2
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:76
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Amazon woodcutters fell trees and jungle preservers will plant them. The "
"resulting logs are used by the stone carver. The charcoal kiln also needs "
"logs to produce charcoal."
msgstr "Les llenyataires amazones tallen arbres i les conservadores de la jungla en planten. Els troncs els fan servir els tallistes. El kiln de carbó també en necessita per produir carbó."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an atlantean ware: Granite, part 1
#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Granite, part 1
#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a frisian ware: Granite, part 1
#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an empire ware: Granite, part 1
#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a barbarian ware: Granite, part 1
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:87
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/atlanteans/units.lua:338
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/barbarians/units.lua:87
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/empire/units.lua:80
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/frisians/units.lua:99
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Granite is a basic building material."
msgstr "El granit és un material de construcció bàsic."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Granite, part 2
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:89
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"The Amazons use granite for making tools and weapons as well. It is produced"
" by the stonecutters and in stone mines."
msgstr "Les amazones usen granit per fer eines i armes. El produeixen les pedreres a les mines de pedra."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Balsa
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:100
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Balsa wood is an important building material. It is also used to make light "
"armor. Balsa trees are cut by an experienced woodcutter."
msgstr "La fusta balsa és un material de construcció important. També s'usa per construir armadures lleugeres. Els arbres balsa els poden tallar llenyataires expertes."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Ironwood
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:111
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"This very hard wood is as hard as iron and it is used for several buildings,"
" tools and weapons. It is cut by a very experienced woodcutter."
msgstr "Aquesta fusta és dura com el ferro i s'empra per fer edificis, eines i armes. Només la poden taller els llenyataires amb experiència."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Rubber
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:122
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Rubber is important for making warriors’ armor and shoes. Rubber trees are "
"collected by experienced woodcutters."
msgstr "El cautxú és important per fer armadures i calçat pels guerrers. S'obté dels arbres de cautxú gràcies als llenyataires amb experiència."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Liana
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:132
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid "Lianas grow on trees. Very durable ropes are made out of them."
msgstr "Les lianes creixen als arbres. Se'n poden fer cordes molt resistents."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Rope
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:142
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"This rope is made out of lianas. It is used for armor dresses and to "
"construct buildings and ships."
msgstr "Les cordes es fabriquen amb lianes. S'usa per a les armadures i per construir edificis i vaixells."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an atlantean ware: Water, part 1
#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Water, part 1
#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a frisian ware: Water, part 1
#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an empire ware: Water, part 1
#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a barbarian ware: Water, part 1
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:155
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/atlanteans/units.lua:436
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/barbarians/units.lua:169
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/empire/units.lua:161
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/frisians/units.lua:166
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Water is the essence of life!"
msgstr "L'aigua és essencial per a la vida!"

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Water, part 2
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:157
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Water is used by the cassava root cooker, the chocolate brewery, the gold "
"digger and the tapir farm."
msgstr "L'aigua s'usa als forns de tapioca, a les fermentadores de xocolata i a les granges de tapirs. També n'usen les excavadores d'or."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Cassava Root
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:167
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Cassava roots are a special kind of root produced at cassava root "
"plantations. The Amazons like their strong taste for making bread and they "
"also feed their tapirs with them."
msgstr "La tapioca són unes arrels especials produïdes a les plantacions de mandioca. A les amazones els agrada els seu gust fort per fer-ne pa i també per alimentar els tapirs."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Cocoa Beans
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:177
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Cocoa beans are gathered from cocoa trees by a cocoa farmer. They are used "
"for producing chocolate."
msgstr "Els grans de cacau es recullen dels arbres de cacau pel cultivador de cacau. S'usen per produir xocolata."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Bread
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:188
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"This tasty bread is made in cassava root cookeries out of cassava root and "
"water. It is the basic ingredient of a ration that is made by a food "
"preserver. Soldiers like it too."
msgstr "Aquest pa saborós es fa als forns de tapioca amb les arrels de la mandioca i d'aigua. És l'ingredient bàsic de les racions que preparen les conservadores de menjar. A les soldades també els agrada."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Chocolate
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:199
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Chocolate is produced by chocolate breweries and used to train soldiers."
msgstr "La xocolata es produeix a les fermentadores de xocolata i s'usa per entrenar soldades."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Fish
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:209
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Fish is one of the two major food resources of the Amazons. It is used by "
"the food preserver to prepare rations for the workers digging for gold dust "
"and granite. It is also consumed at the training sites (training glade and "
"warriors’ gathering) and for recruiting new soldiers."
msgstr "El peix és una de les dues fonts alimentàries de les amazones. L'usa la conservadora de menjar per preparar racions per a les treballadores que extreuen pols d'or i el granit. També es consumeix als llocs d'entrenament (als clars d'entrenament i als punts de trobada dels guerrers) i per reclutar soldades."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Meat, part 1
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:219
msgctxt "ware"
msgid ""
"Meat contains a lot of energy, and it is obtained from wild game taken by "
"hunter-gatherers."
msgstr "La carn conté molta energia i s'obté d'animals salvatges que cacen els recol·lectors i caçadors."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Meat, part 2
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:221
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Meat is used by the food preserver to prepare rations for the workers "
"digging for gold dust and granite. It is also consumed at the training sites"
" (training glade and warriors’ gathering) and for recruiting new soldiers."
msgstr "La carn l'usa la conservadora de menjar per preparar racions per les treballadores que extreuen pols d'or i granit. També es consumeix als llocs d'entrenament (als clars d'entrenament i als punts de trobada dels guerrers) i per reclutar soldats."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Ration, part 1
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:232
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"A small bite to keep the workers digging for gold dust and granite strong "
"and working. The scout also consumes rations on her scouting trips."
msgstr "Una mica de menjar que manté fortes i ajuda a treballar les encarregades d'extreure granit i pols d'or. L'exploradora també en necessita per als seus viatges d'exploració."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Ration, part 2
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:234
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Rations are produced by the food preserver out of fish or meat and bread. "
"They are dried using a charcoal fire."
msgstr "Les conservadores de menjar produeixen racions a partir de peix o carn i pa. Es sequen al foc del carbó."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Gold Dust, part 1
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:248
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid "Gold dust is washed in a gold digger dwelling."
msgstr "La pols d'or la renta l'excavador d'or."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Gold Dust, part 2
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:250
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Smelted in a furnace, it turns into gold which is used as a precious "
"building material and to produce armor."
msgstr "Es redueix a la farga i s'aconsegueixen lingots d'or, que s'utilitzen com un valuós material de construcció i de fabricació d'armadures."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Gold, part 1
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:261
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid "Gold is the most valuable of all metals,"
msgstr "L'or és el metall més valuós,"

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Gold, part 2
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:263
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"and it is smelted out of gold dust. It is produced by the furnace and used "
"by the dressmaker and for special buildings."
msgstr "i s'obté un cop fosa la pols d'or. Es produeix a la farga i l'usa la sastressa i alguns edificis especials."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Charcoal, part 1
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:274
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Charcoal produced out of logs by a charcoal burner. The Amazons use charcoal"
" for drying their food and for smelting gold."
msgstr "El carbó es pot produir amb troncs gràcies a les carboneres. Les amazones produeixen carbó per assecar el seu menjar i fondre or."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Pick
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:288
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid "Picks are used by stonecutters to cut granite from rocks or in mines."
msgstr "Els pics l'usen els tallistes per tallar granit a les mines i a les roques de l'exterior."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Felling Ax, part 1
#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a frisian ware: Felling Ax, part 1
#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an empire ware: Felling Ax, part 1
#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a barbarian ware: Felling Ax, part 1
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:299
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/barbarians/units.lua:332
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/empire/units.lua:349
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/frisians/units.lua:396
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "The felling ax is the tool to chop down trees."
msgstr "La destral és l'eina per talar arbres."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Felling Ax, part 2
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:301
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid "It is used by a woodcutter and produced by the stone carver."
msgstr "L'usa el llenyataire i el produeix el tallista."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an atlantean ware: Shovel, part 1
#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Shovel, part 1
#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a frisian ware: Shovel, part 1
#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an empire ware: Shovel, part 1
#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a barbarian ware: Shovel, part 1
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:312
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/atlanteans/units.lua:599
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/barbarians/units.lua:345
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/empire/units.lua:371
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/frisians/units.lua:409
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "Shovels are needed for the proper handling of plants."
msgstr "Les pales són necessàries per plantar arbres i plantes adequadament."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Shovel, part 2
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:314
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Therefore the jungle preservers, the cassava farmers and the cocoa farmers "
"use them. They are produced by the stone carver."
msgstr "Per això, l'usen les conservadores de la jungla, les cultivadores de mandioca i les cultivadores de cacau. Les produeixen els tallistes."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an atlantean ware: Hammer, part 1
#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Hammer, part 1
#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a frisian ware: Hammer, part 1
#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an empire ware: Hammer, part 1
#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for a barbarian ware: Hammer, part 1
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:325
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/atlanteans/units.lua:612
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/barbarians/units.lua:358
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/empire/units.lua:384
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/frisians/units.lua:422
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "The hammer is an essential tool."
msgstr "El martell és una eina essencial."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Hammer, part 2
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:327
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Geologists, builders, shipwrights and stone carvers all need a hammer. Make "
"sure you’ve always got some in reserve! They are produced by the stone "
"carver."
msgstr "Les geòlogues, constructores, mestres d'aixa i tallistes necessiten un martell. Assegureu-vos que en teniu de reserva! Els produeixen les tallistes."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Machete
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:338
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid "The machete is the tool of the liana cutters."
msgstr "El matxet és l'eina dels talladors de lianes."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Wooden Spear, part 1
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:349
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"This spear is the basic weapon in the Amazon military system. It is produced"
" by the stone carver. In combination with a tunic, it is the equipment to "
"fit out young soldiers."
msgstr "Aquesta llança és l'arma bàsica del sistema militar de les amazones. Les produeix el tallista i, juntament amb una túnica, és l'equipament de les soldades novells."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Wooden Spear, part 2
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:351
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid "It is used by the amazon hunter-gatherers as well."
msgstr "També l'usen les recol·lectores i caçadores amazones."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Chisel, part 1
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:362
msgctxt "ware"
msgid "The chisel is an essential tool."
msgstr "El cisell és una eina essencial."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Chisel, part 2
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:364
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Stone carvers need a chisel. Make sure you’ve always got some in reserve! "
"They are produced by the stone carvers themselves."
msgstr "Els tallistes necessiten un cisell. Assegureu-vos que sempre en teniu de reserva! Els produeixen els mateixos tallistes."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Kitchen Tools
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:375
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Kitchen tools are needed for preparing rations, baking cassava bread and "
"brewing chocolate. Be sure to have a stone carver to produce this basic "
"tool."
msgstr "Les eines de cuina són necessàries per preparar racions, fornejar el pa de tapioca i fermentar xocolata. Assegureu-vos de tenir un tallista que pugui produir aquesta eina bàsica."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Needles
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:386
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Needles are used by dressmakers to make dresses, boots and armor for the "
"soldiers."
msgstr "Les sastresses necessiten agulles per fer vestits, calçat i armadures per a les soldades."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Stone Bowl
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:397
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid "Stone bowls are used to wash gold and to smelt gold dust."
msgstr "Els bols de pedra serveixen per rentar i fondre la pols d'or."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Stone Tipped Spear
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:411
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"This spear has a stone spike. It is produced in a stone workshop and used in"
" a warriors’ gathering – together with food – to train soldiers from attack "
"level 0 to attack level 1."
msgstr "Aquestes llances tenen una punta de pedra. Són produïdes al taller de pedra i s'empren en els punts de trobada de guerrers juntament amb menjar per entrenar el nivell d'atac de les soldades de nivell 0 a nivell 1."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Hardened Spear
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:422
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"This is a hardened spear with a stone tip. It is produced in a stone "
"workshop and used in a warriors’ gathering – together with food – to train "
"soldiers from attack level 1 to level 2."
msgstr "Aquesta llança endurida té una punta de pedra. Es produeix al taller de pedra i s'usa als punts de trobada de guerrers juntament amb menjar per entrenar l'atac de les soldades de nivell 1 a nivell 2."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Wooden Armor
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:433
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"This light wooden armor is a basic piece of armor for the Amazons’ soldiers."
" It is produced by a dressmaker and used in a training glade – together with"
" food – to train soldiers from health level 0 to level 1."
msgstr "Les armadures lleugeres de fusta són una peça bàsica de l'armadura de les soldades amazones. Les produeixen les sastresses i s'usen en els camps d'entrenament juntament amb menjar per entrenar la salut de les soldades de nivell 0 a nivell 1."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Wodden Helmet
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:444
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"A wooden helmet is a basic piece of equipment for protecting soldiers. It is"
" produced by the dressmaker and used to train soldiers from health level 1 "
"to level 2."
msgstr "Els cascos de fusta són una peça d'equipament bàsic per protegir les soldades. Els produeixen les sastresses i s'usen per entrenar la salut de les soldades de nivell 1 a nivell 2."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Warrior's Coat
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:455
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Ordinary tunics can be decorated and reinforced with gold and wood chunks. "
"Such tunics are the best armor."
msgstr "Les túniques ordinàries es poden decorar i reforçar amb or i trossos de fusta. Aquestes túniques són la millor armadura dels amazònics."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Tunic
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:466
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Rubber can be bound into a tunic, which is used as basic armor. All new "
"soldiers are clothed in a tunic."
msgstr "El cautxú es pot afegir a les túniques, que són una armadura bàsica. Totes les soldades porten túniques. "

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Padded Vest
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:477
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Padded vests are light but durable armor. They are produced by the "
"dressmaker and used to train soldiers’ defence from level 0 to level 1."
msgstr "Les armilles encoixinades són lleugeres però també són una armadura duradora. Les produeixen les sastresses i s'usen per entrenar la defensa de les soldades de nivell 0 a nivell 1."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Padded Protector
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:488
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Padded protectors are strong and durable armor. They are produced by the "
"dressmaker and used to train soldiers’ defence from level 1 to level 2."
msgstr "Els protectors encoixinats són una armadura forta i duradora. Les produeixen les sastresses i s'usen per entrenar la defensa de les soldades de nivell 1 a nivell 2."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Sturdy Boots
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:499
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Sturdy boots are excellent footwear for soldiers to be quicker on their "
"feet. They are produced by the dressmaker and used to train soldiers’ evade "
"from level 0 to level 1."
msgstr "Les botes robustes són un calçat excel·lent per moure's més ràpid. Les produeixen les sastresses i s'usen per entrenar l'evasió de les soldades de nivell 0 a nivell 1."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Swift Boots
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:510
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Swift boots are light and durable footwear for soldiers to be quicker on "
"their feet. They are produced by the dressmaker and used to train soldiers’ "
"evade from level 1 to level 2."
msgstr "Les botes lleugeres són un calçat de les soldades perquè puguin moure's més ràpid. Les produeixen les sastresses i s'usen per entrenar l'evasió de les soldades de nivell 1 a nivell 2."

#. TRANSLATORS: Helptext for an amazon ware: Hero Boots
#: ../../data/tribes/initialization/amazons/units.lua:521
msgctxt "amazons_ware"
msgid ""
"Hero boots! The only suitable footwear for a real hero. They are produced by"
" the dressmaker and used to train soldiers’ evade from level 2 to level 3."
